We'll be publishing a new SaaS YouTube study at Grizzle soon.The report covers an analysis of 3,623 videos across 71 SaaS channels, as well as AIO events across 873 keywords and queries.Some early findings:--> YouTube videos appear in AIOs for 74.9% of SaaS keywords and queries that triggered an AIO event.--> Across 542 BOFU keywords, YouTube appeared in the AIOs 75.1% of the time.--> Of 138 branded keywords in our dataset, the YouTube channels of our 71 tracked brands only appeared in 0.7% of those queries.The study also covers:Winning and losing title patterns across titles, thumbnails, content formats, YouTube Shorts, and more.

